{"tid":382783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"布志綸 重壞音樂懷抱，用歌聲唱出人生各種辛酸，走出迷路，打破舊有形象","createTime":"2017-09-01T03:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T07:45:02.000Z","uid":31561,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"091526da6cc6db08604f5a1466e9a3ee0444ed14","tid":382783,"uid":31561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"《人在野》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/111543_d03dc22e89ef75c18f772e77bf0a5e4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F111543_d03dc22e89ef75c18f772e77bf0a5e4f.png&h=b53ef35a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們總避免不了人生路上的荊棘，但別忘記願意伴你一起穿過叢林走到平原的人。人在野是一個狀況一個處景；但亦是一種心態，一種面對逆境的想法。每個人也曾面對困難迷失的時候，人在野想帶出的意義，就是告訴大家：你並非孤獨一人。不論是男女朋友、丈夫、老婆、小孩、朋友、知音人，世界上總有人會明白和願意伴你一起面對任何困難，<br />\n所以，請找出並珍惜那一個「他/她」。<br />\n<br />\n自我修行。等待，是為了走更遠的路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rH2wggjazSo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrH2wggjazSo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=BLlKhgiluzO1BPJg9M7OM54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bd63afd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rH2wggjazSo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"37ffaae4d85d7d834b427a8f831fe61f70c0b8d0","tid":382783,"uid":31561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"真係好用心機去做音樂"},{"pid":"6b3d0866d4dd583eac50cc14800bed0de4a502c2","tid":382783,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"無做過點認啫"},{"pid":"bc58493933057ba795669c2bf816299fd6312757","tid":382783,"uid":31561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"其實大家聽歌係用隻耳，可唔可以先聽左再決定點諗呢"},{"pid":"1fc3cf89d99b0d2ba05fd72e012e2f0b8ed7c6d9","tid":382783,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"好聽<br />\n好有意思既一首歌<img 